# Welcome!

Contributions are very welcome on the ${project.name}. When contributing please keep this in mind:

- Open an issue to discuss new bigger features.
- Write code consistent with the project style and make sure the tests are passing.
- Stay in touch with us if we have follow up questions or requests for further changes.

# Development

The source for this project is found in GitHub at ${project.url}.

The project is developed using Maven and builds under Java ${context.get("jdk.version")}.

All code must include an Apache license header.  Any header that passes the [Apache RAT](https://creadur.apache.org/rat/) tests is acceptable.  The RAT check is automatically run during build.  We recommend the following text block for licenses.

```java
